{"id":"api/forms/Validators","title":"驗證器","contents":"<article>\n  <div class=\"breadcrumb-container\">\n    <div class=\"breadcrumb\">\n      <script type=\"application/ld+json\">\n        {\n          \"@context\": \"http://schema.org\",\n          \"@type\": \"BreadcrumbList\",\n          \"itemListElement\": [\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 1, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api\", \"name\": \"API\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 2, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api/forms\", \"name\": \"@angular/forms\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 3, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api/forms/Validators\", \"name\": \"Validators\" } }\n          ]\n        }\n      </script>\n        <a href=\"/api\">API</a> &gt; <a href=\"api/forms\">@angular/forms</a>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/17.3.0-next.1/packages/forms/src/validators.ts#L128-L438\" aria-label=\"檢視原始碼\" title=\"檢視原始碼\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n  </div>\n  <header class=\"api-header\">\n    <h1 id=\"validators\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"6eslvgi18whex64cqo11onnlk\">驗證器<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/forms/Validators#validators\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n    <label class=\"api-type-label class\">class</label>\n    <label class=\"github-links api-status-label final\" title=\"此類不可派生。\">\n      <a href=\"https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/17.3.0-next.1/docs/PUBLIC_API.md#final-classes\">最終類</a>\n    </label>\n  </header>\n  \n\n  <div class=\"api-body\">\n  <section class=\"short-description\">\n    <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"547cyu3tijlphwc3qx56fzt8c\">提供一組內建驗證器，可用於各種表單控制元件。</p>\n\n    <p><a href=\"api/forms/Validators#description\">檢視更多...</a></p>\n  </section><section class=\"class-overview\">\n<code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\">\nclass <a href=\"api/forms/Validators\" class=\"code-anchor\">Validators</a> {\n  <a class=\"code-anchor\" href=\"api/forms/Validators#min\">static <span class=\"member-name\">min</span>(min: number): ValidatorFn</a>\n  <a class=\"code-anchor\" href=\"api/forms/Validators#max\">static <span class=\"member-name\">max</span>(max: number): ValidatorFn</a>\n  <a class=\"code-anchor\" href=\"api/forms/Validators#required\">static <span class=\"member-name\">required</span>(control: AbstractControl&lt;any, any&gt;): ValidationErrors | null</a>\n  <a class=\"code-anchor\" href=\"api/forms/Validators#requiredTrue\">static <span class=\"member-name\">requiredTrue</span>(control: AbstractControl&lt;any, any&gt;): ValidationErrors | null</a>\n  <a class=\"code-anchor\" href=\"api/forms/Validators#email\">static <span class=\"member-name\">email</span>(control: AbstractControl&lt;any, any&gt;): ValidationErrors | null</a>\n  <a class=\"code-anchor\" href=\"api/forms/Validators#minLength\">static <span class=\"member-name\">minLength</span>(minLength: number): ValidatorFn</a>\n  <a class=\"code-anchor\" href=\"api/forms/Validators#maxLength\">static <span class=\"member-name\">maxLength</span>(maxLength: number): ValidatorFn</a>\n  <a class=\"code-anchor\" href=\"api/forms/Validators#pattern\">static <span class=\"member-name\">pattern</span>(pattern: string | RegExp): ValidatorFn</a>\n  <a class=\"code-anchor\" href=\"api/forms/Validators#nullValidator\">static <span class=\"member-name\">nullValidator</span>(control: AbstractControl&lt;any, any&gt;): ValidationErrors | null</a>\n  <a class=\"code-anchor\" href=\"api/forms/Validators#compose\">static <span class=\"member-name\">compose</span>(validators: ValidatorFn[]): ValidatorFn | null</a>\n  <a class=\"code-anchor\" href=\"api/forms/Validators#composeAsync\">static <span class=\"member-name\">composeAsync</span>(validators: AsyncValidatorFn[]): AsyncValidatorFn | null</a>\n}\n</code-example>\n\n</section>\n\n<section class=\"see-also\">\n  <h2 id=\"see-also\">參見<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/forms/Validators#see-also\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <ul>\n    <li><p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"cctgm036006j67c32lscy3pom\"><a href=\"/guide/form-validation\">表單驗證</a></p></li>\n  </ul>\n</section>\n  \n<section class=\"description\">\n  <h2 id=\"description\">說明<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/forms/Validators#description\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"1vcl8w7pfm8k7gbktnio6vbk4\">驗證器就是一個函式，它可以處理單個 <code><a href=\"api/forms/FormControl\" class=\"code-anchor\">FormControl</a></code> 或一組控制元件，並回傳一個錯誤對映表（map）或\nnull。null 表示驗證已透過了。</p>\n</section>\n  \n<section class=\"static-methods\">\n  <h2 id=\"static-methods\">靜態方法<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/forms/Validators#static-methods\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <a id=\"min\"></a>\n<table class=\"is-full-width method-table static-method\">\n  <thead><tr><th>\n    <div class=\"with-github-links\">\n      <h3 id=\"min\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"d1sr4ktkknccbvw7rjdmsnd50\">min()<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/forms/Validators#min\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h3>\n      <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/17.3.0-next.1/packages/forms/src/validators.ts#L141-L163\" aria-label=\"檢視原始碼\" title=\"檢視原始碼\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n    </div>\n  </th></tr></thead>\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <td class=\"short-description\">\n        <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"6n0djaynbhfs7fulxxeta37na\">此驗證器要求控制元件的值大於或等於指定的數字。\n它只有函式形式，沒有指令形式。</p>\n\n        <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"ajvz2kusfoda7eq5p74uu34f3\">另請參閱:</p>\n        <ul>\n          <li><a href=\"api/forms/AbstractControl#updateValueAndValidity\"><code>updateValueAndValidity</code></a>\n</li>\n        </ul>\n        </td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>\n        <div class=\"overload-info\">\n  <code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"no-box api-heading\"><a href=\"api/upgrade/static\" class=\"code-anchor\">static</a> <span class=\"member-name\"><a href=\"api/forms/MinValidator\" class=\"code-anchor\">min</a></span>(<a href=\"api/forms/MinValidator\" class=\"code-anchor\">min</a>: number): <a href=\"api/forms/ValidatorFn\" class=\"code-anchor\">ValidatorFn</a></code-example>\n\n  <h6 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"parameters\">引數</h6>\n  <table class=\"is-full-width list-table parameters-table static-method-overload-parameters\">\n  <tbody>\n    <tr class=\"static-method-overload-parameter\">\n      <td class=\"param-name\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"dpjiqlbb0ty82hq3di2vrm9sg\"><a id=\"\"></a>\n        <code><a href=\"api/forms/MinValidator\" class=\"code-anchor\">min</a></code></td>\n      <td class=\"param-type\"><code>number</code></td>\n      <td class=\"param-description\">\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n  <h6 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"returns\">回傳值</h6>\n  <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"3m8rl7bf850bcbrd0keuepycr\">如果驗證失敗，則此驗證器函式回傳一個帶有 <code><a href=\"api/forms/MinValidator\" class=\"code-anchor\">min</a></code> 屬性的對映表（map），否則為 <code>null</code>。</p>\n\n</div>\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td class=\"usage-notes\">\n        <h4 id=\"min-usage-notes\">使用說明<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/forms/Validators#min-usage-notes\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h4>\n        <h5 id=\"validate-against-a-minimum-of-3\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"eu7qdwsx947sfha4jtwtx2qwd\">驗證至少為3<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/forms/Validators#validate-against-a-minimum-of-3\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h5>\n<code-example language=\"typescript\">\nconst control = new <a href=\"api/forms/FormControl\" class=\"code-anchor\">FormControl</a>(2, Validators.min(3));\n\nconsole.log(control.errors); // {<a href=\"api/forms/MinValidator\" class=\"code-anchor\">min</a>: {<a href=\"api/forms/MinValidator\" class=\"code-anchor\">min</a>: 3, actual: 2}}\n</code-example>\n\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n  <a id=\"max\"></a>\n<table class=\"is-full-width method-table static-method\">\n  <thead><tr><th>\n    <div class=\"with-github-links\">\n      <h3 id=\"max\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"5wtk31li4hp7iusfx76y8npp4\">max()<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/forms/Validators#max\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h3>\n      <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/17.3.0-next.1/packages/forms/src/validators.ts#L164-L187\" aria-label=\"檢視原始碼\" title=\"檢視原始碼\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n    </div>\n  </th></tr></thead>\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <td class=\"short-description\">\n        <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"e97o1wxsu1mnn3uqxbhyyomdg\">此驗證器要求控制元件的值小於等於指定的數字。\n它只有函式形式，沒有指令形式。</p>\n\n        <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"ajvz2kusfoda7eq5p74uu34f3\">另請參閱:</p>\n        <ul>\n          <li><a href=\"api/forms/AbstractControl#updateValueAndValidity\"><code>updateValueAndValidity</code></a>\n</li>\n        </ul>\n        </td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>\n        <div class=\"overload-info\">\n  <code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"no-box api-heading\"><a href=\"api/upgrade/static\" class=\"code-anchor\">static</a> <span class=\"member-name\"><a href=\"api/forms/MaxValidator\" class=\"code-anchor\">max</a></span>(<a href=\"api/forms/MaxValidator\" class=\"code-anchor\">max</a>: number): <a href=\"api/forms/ValidatorFn\" class=\"code-anchor\">ValidatorFn</a></code-example>\n\n  <h6 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"parameters\">引數</h6>\n  <table class=\"is-full-width list-table parameters-table static-method-overload-parameters\">\n  <tbody>\n    <tr class=\"static-method-overload-parameter\">\n      <td class=\"param-name\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"a2imflvrtwiefn6ce5fkmc0fb\"><a id=\"\"></a>\n        <code><a href=\"api/forms/MaxValidator\" class=\"code-anchor\">max</a></code></td>\n      <td class=\"param-type\"><code>number</code></td>\n      <td class=\"param-description\">\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n  <h6 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"returns\">回傳值</h6>\n  <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"42obenwdfulpfma8a7bsaov19\">如果驗證失敗，則此驗證器函式回傳一個帶有 <code><a href=\"api/forms/MaxValidator\" class=\"code-anchor\">max</a></code> 屬性的對映表（map），否則為 <code>null</code>。</p>\n\n</div>\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td class=\"usage-notes\">\n        <h4 id=\"max-usage-notes\">使用說明<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/forms/Validators#max-usage-notes\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h4>\n        <h5 id=\"validate-against-a-maximum-of-15\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"86bcr8ztjalcvx9bf62s1l4l4\">驗證至多為15<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/forms/Validators#validate-against-a-maximum-of-15\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h5>\n<code-example language=\"typescript\">\nconst control = new <a href=\"api/forms/FormControl\" class=\"code-anchor\">FormControl</a>(16, Validators.max(15));\n\nconsole.log(control.errors); // {<a href=\"api/forms/MaxValidator\" class=\"code-anchor\">max</a>: {<a href=\"api/forms/MaxValidator\" class=\"code-anchor\">max</a>: 15, actual: 16}}\n</code-example>\n\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n  <a id=\"required\"></a>\n<table class=\"is-full-width method-table static-method\">\n  <thead><tr><th>\n    <div class=\"with-github-links\">\n      <h3 id=\"required\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"bi3hluo16khip4ig06ruz8sw5\">required()<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/forms/Validators#required\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h3>\n      <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/17.3.0-next.1/packages/forms/src/validators.ts#L188-L211\" aria-label=\"檢視原始碼\" title=\"檢視原始碼\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n    </div>\n  </th></tr></thead>\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <td class=\"short-description\">\n        <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"av2o3m6k8yhro7q33k0tax1t2\">此驗證器要求控制元件具有非空值。</p>\n\n        <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"ajvz2kusfoda7eq5p74uu34f3\">另請參閱:</p>\n        <ul>\n          <li><a href=\"api/forms/AbstractControl#updateValueAndValidity\"><code>updateValueAndValidity</code></a>\n</li>\n        </ul>\n        </td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>\n        <div class=\"overload-info\">\n  <code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"no-box api-heading\"><a href=\"api/upgrade/static\" class=\"code-anchor\">static</a> <span class=\"member-name\">required</span>(control: <a href=\"api/forms/AbstractControl\" class=\"code-anchor\">AbstractControl</a>&lt;any, any&gt;): <a href=\"api/forms/ValidationErrors\" class=\"code-anchor\">ValidationErrors</a> | null</code-example>\n\n  <h6 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"parameters\">引數</h6>\n  <table class=\"is-full-width list-table parameters-table static-method-overload-parameters\">\n  <tbody>\n    <tr class=\"static-method-overload-parameter\">\n      <td class=\"param-name\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"96j43ie9c8s2bdcichcwyw0vj\"><a id=\"\"></a>\n        <code>control</code></td>\n      <td class=\"param-type\"><code><a href=\"api/forms/AbstractControl\" class=\"code-anchor\">AbstractControl</a>&lt;any, any&gt;</code></td>\n      <td class=\"param-description\">\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n  <h6 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"returns\">回傳值</h6>\n  <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"6fjhdcceg1d0crreoozm4sb5z\">如果驗證失敗，則此驗證器函式回傳一個帶有 <code>required</code> 屬性的對映表（map），否則為 <code>null</code>。</p>\n\n</div>\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td class=\"usage-notes\">\n        <h4 id=\"required-usage-notes\">使用說明<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/forms/Validators#required-usage-notes\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h4>\n        <h5 id=\"validate-that-the-field-is-non-empty\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"cp3bs0ak5cns4agdst01b81r1\">驗證欄位不能為空<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/forms/Validators#validate-that-the-field-is-non-empty\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h5>\n<code-example language=\"typescript\">\nconst control = new <a href=\"api/forms/FormControl\" class=\"code-anchor\">FormControl</a>('', Validators.required);\n\nconsole.log(control.errors); // {required: true}\n</code-example>\n\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n  <a id=\"requiredTrue\"></a>\n<table class=\"is-full-width method-table static-method\">\n  <thead><tr><th>\n    <div class=\"with-github-links\">\n      <h3 id=\"requiredtrue\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"1v9mwcp7zbqz4da0l9w1a7y06\">requiredTrue()<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/forms/Validators#requiredtrue\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h3>\n      <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/17.3.0-next.1/packages/forms/src/validators.ts#L212-L236\" aria-label=\"檢視原始碼\" title=\"檢視原始碼\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n    </div>\n  </th></tr></thead>\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <td class=\"short-description\">\n        <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"7aclbstzljj8jvhwk11gwcd5m\">此驗證器要求控制元件的值為真。它通常用來驗證檢查框。</p>\n\n        <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"ajvz2kusfoda7eq5p74uu34f3\">另請參閱:</p>\n        <ul>\n          <li><a href=\"api/forms/AbstractControl#updateValueAndValidity\"><code>updateValueAndValidity</code></a>\n</li>\n        </ul>\n        </td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>\n        <div class=\"overload-info\">\n  <code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"no-box api-heading\"><a href=\"api/upgrade/static\" class=\"code-anchor\">static</a> <span class=\"member-name\">requiredTrue</span>(control: <a href=\"api/forms/AbstractControl\" class=\"code-anchor\">AbstractControl</a>&lt;any, any&gt;): <a href=\"api/forms/ValidationErrors\" class=\"code-anchor\">ValidationErrors</a> | null</code-example>\n\n  <h6 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"parameters\">引數</h6>\n  <table class=\"is-full-width list-table parameters-table static-method-overload-parameters\">\n  <tbody>\n    <tr class=\"static-method-overload-parameter\">\n      <td class=\"param-name\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"96j43ie9c8s2bdcichcwyw0vj\"><a id=\"\"></a>\n        <code>control</code></td>\n      <td class=\"param-type\"><code><a href=\"api/forms/AbstractControl\" class=\"code-anchor\">AbstractControl</a>&lt;any, any&gt;</code></td>\n      <td class=\"param-description\">\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n  <h6 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"returns\">回傳值</h6>\n  <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"d1rhbch8ff731h8du22tx87l\">如果驗證失敗，則此驗證器函式回傳一個帶有 <code>required</code> 屬性、值為 <code>true</code> 的對映表（map），否則為\n<code>null</code>。</p>\n\n</div>\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td class=\"usage-notes\">\n        <h4 id=\"requiredTrue-usage-notes\">使用說明<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/forms/Validators#requiredTrue-usage-notes\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h4>\n        <h5 id=\"validate-that-the-field-value-is-true\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"dw7a6s98m309qzaxjm52odnb6\">驗證欄位值為true<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/forms/Validators#validate-that-the-field-value-is-true\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h5>\n<code-example language=\"typescript\">\nconst control = new <a href=\"api/forms/FormControl\" class=\"code-anchor\">FormControl</a>('some value', Validators.requiredTrue);\n\nconsole.log(control.errors); // {required: true}\n</code-example>\n\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n  <a id=\"email\"></a>\n<table class=\"is-full-width method-table static-method\">\n  <thead><tr><th>\n    <div class=\"with-github-links\">\n      <h3 id=\"email\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"573nm21yb9llnh65uwemyif5x\">email()<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/forms/Validators#email\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h3>\n      <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/17.3.0-next.1/packages/forms/src/validators.ts#L237-L276\" aria-label=\"檢視原始碼\" title=\"檢視原始碼\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n    </div>\n  </th></tr></thead>\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <td class=\"short-description\">\n        <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"3tfljqzz1ncn84rurl36v9vgx\">此驗證器要求控制元件的值能透過 email 格式驗證。</p>\n\n        <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"ajvz2kusfoda7eq5p74uu34f3\">另請參閱:</p>\n        <ul>\n          <li><a href=\"api/forms/AbstractControl#updateValueAndValidity\"><code>updateValueAndValidity</code></a>\n</li>\n        </ul>\n        </td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>\n        <div class=\"overload-info\">\n  <code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"no-box api-heading\"><a href=\"api/upgrade/static\" class=\"code-anchor\">static</a> <span class=\"member-name\"><a href=\"api/forms/EmailValidator\" class=\"code-anchor\">email</a></span>(control: <a href=\"api/forms/AbstractControl\" class=\"code-anchor\">AbstractControl</a>&lt;any, any&gt;): <a href=\"api/forms/ValidationErrors\" class=\"code-anchor\">ValidationErrors</a> | null</code-example>\n\n  <h6 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"parameters\">引數</h6>\n  <table class=\"is-full-width list-table parameters-table static-method-overload-parameters\">\n  <tbody>\n    <tr class=\"static-method-overload-parameter\">\n      <td class=\"param-name\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"96j43ie9c8s2bdcichcwyw0vj\"><a id=\"\"></a>\n        <code>control</code></td>\n      <td class=\"param-type\"><code><a href=\"api/forms/AbstractControl\" class=\"code-anchor\">AbstractControl</a>&lt;any, any&gt;</code></td>\n      <td class=\"param-description\">\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n  <h6 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"returns\">回傳值</h6>\n  <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"8zg9jvryxpy08ikhqoni2skad\">如果驗證失敗，則此驗證器函式回傳一個帶有 <code><a href=\"api/forms/EmailValidator\" class=\"code-anchor\">email</a></code> 屬性的對映表（map），否則為 <code>null</code>。</p>\n\n</div>\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td class=\"description\">\n        <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"1lx4gn5yjxdxpv574rx4xztix\">使用適合普通用例的<a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Guide/Regular_Expressions\">正則表示式模式測試值</a>。該模式基於\n<a href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/input.html#valid-e-mail-address\">WHATWG HTML\n規範</a>中有效電子郵件地址的定義，並進行了一些增強以支援更多的\nRFC 規則（比如與網域名稱相關的規則以及地址不同部分的長度）。</p>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"9oac06p7h2zyese85nj4xzi8z\">與 WHATWG 版本的區別包括：</p>\n<ul>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"94o6y41cqr2yaoqeyaan70ta0\">禁止 <code>local-part</code>（<code>@</code> 符號前面的部分）以句點（<code>.</code>）開頭或結尾。</li>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"ces1ciq4k7oy7sw07aoq3s5xz\">不允許 <code>local-part</code> 超過 64 個字元。</li>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"3k30b39k90jkoi0hb8oeky2be\">不允許整個地址超過 254 個字元。</li>\n</ul>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"a2ythaa8lhkdsrtlc44aom866\">如果此模式不能滿足你的業務需求，則可以使用 <code><a href=\"api/forms/Validators#pattern\" class=\"code-anchor\">Validators.pattern()</a></code> 來針對其他模式驗證值。</p>\n\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td class=\"usage-notes\">\n        <h4 id=\"email-usage-notes\">使用說明<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/forms/Validators#email-usage-notes\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h4>\n        <h5 id=\"validate-that-the-field-matches-a-valid-email-pattern\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"dcvpalra82hvm8vpwlmzav424\">驗證該欄位對應有效的 email 格式。<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/forms/Validators#validate-that-the-field-matches-a-valid-email-pattern\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h5>\n<code-example language=\"typescript\">\nconst control = new <a href=\"api/forms/FormControl\" class=\"code-anchor\">FormControl</a>('bad@', Validators.email);\n\nconsole.log(control.errors); // {<a href=\"api/forms/EmailValidator\" class=\"code-anchor\">email</a>: true}\n</code-example>\n\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n  <a id=\"minLength\"></a>\n<table class=\"is-full-width method-table static-method\">\n  <thead><tr><th>\n    <div class=\"with-github-links\">\n      <h3 id=\"minlength\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"bozep9qyya0q2zaduvclo05ut\">minLength()<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/forms/Validators#minlength\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h3>\n      <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/17.3.0-next.1/packages/forms/src/validators.ts#L277-L310\" aria-label=\"檢視原始碼\" title=\"檢視原始碼\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n    </div>\n  </th></tr></thead>\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <td class=\"short-description\">\n        <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"3kmma49wdii888xk551iuxuxw\">此驗證器要求控制元件值的長度大於等於所指定的最小長度。當使用 HTML5 的 <code><a href=\"api/forms/MinLengthValidator\" class=\"code-anchor\">minlength</a></code>\n屬性時，此驗證器也會生效。</p>\n\n        <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"ajvz2kusfoda7eq5p74uu34f3\">另請參閱:</p>\n        <ul>\n          <li><a href=\"api/forms/AbstractControl#updateValueAndValidity\"><code>updateValueAndValidity</code></a>\n</li>\n        </ul>\n        </td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>\n        <div class=\"overload-info\">\n  <code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"no-box api-heading\"><a href=\"api/upgrade/static\" class=\"code-anchor\">static</a> <span class=\"member-name\">minLength</span>(minLength: number): <a href=\"api/forms/ValidatorFn\" class=\"code-anchor\">ValidatorFn</a></code-example>\n\n  <h6 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"parameters\">引數</h6>\n  <table class=\"is-full-width list-table parameters-table static-method-overload-parameters\">\n  <tbody>\n    <tr class=\"static-method-overload-parameter\">\n      <td class=\"param-name\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"czfun66skeuwvgond2bn992uh\"><a id=\"\"></a>\n        <code>minLength</code></td>\n      <td class=\"param-type\"><code>number</code></td>\n      <td class=\"param-description\">\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n  <h6 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"returns\">回傳值</h6>\n  <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"elbyxk2gdk33fz673y9erok1t\">如果驗證失敗，則此驗證器函式回傳一個帶有 <code><a href=\"api/forms/MinLengthValidator\" class=\"code-anchor\">minlength</a></code> 屬性的對映表（map），否則為 <code>null</code>。</p>\n\n</div>\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td class=\"usage-notes\">\n        <h4 id=\"minLength-usage-notes\">使用說明<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/forms/Validators#minLength-usage-notes\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h4>\n        <h5 id=\"validate-that-the-field-has-a-minimum-of-3-characters\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"5trpf2545mrpusr19tivgclmt\">驗證該欄位至少有 3 個字元<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/forms/Validators#validate-that-the-field-has-a-minimum-of-3-characters\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h5>\n<code-example language=\"typescript\">\nconst control = new <a href=\"api/forms/FormControl\" class=\"code-anchor\">FormControl</a>('ng', Validators.minLength(3));\n\nconsole.log(control.errors); // {<a href=\"api/forms/MinLengthValidator\" class=\"code-anchor\">minlength</a>: {requiredLength: 3, actualLength: 2}}\n</code-example>\n<code-example language=\"html\">\n&lt;input <a href=\"api/forms/MinLengthValidator\" class=\"code-anchor\">minlength</a>=\"5\"&gt;\n</code-example>\n\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n  <a id=\"maxLength\"></a>\n<table class=\"is-full-width method-table static-method\">\n  <thead><tr><th>\n    <div class=\"with-github-links\">\n      <h3 id=\"maxlength\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"9jpietwqkivemtnfhd0tt4312\">maxLength()<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/forms/Validators#maxlength\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h3>\n      <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/17.3.0-next.1/packages/forms/src/validators.ts#L311-L341\" aria-label=\"檢視原始碼\" title=\"檢視原始碼\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n    </div>\n  </th></tr></thead>\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <td class=\"short-description\">\n        <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"236lny7zwv8cqccnampcmg9qx\">此驗證器要求控制元件值的長度小於等於所指定的最大長度。當使用 HTML5 的 <code><a href=\"api/forms/MaxLengthValidator\" class=\"code-anchor\">maxlength</a></code>\n屬性時，此驗證器也會生效。</p>\n\n        <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"ajvz2kusfoda7eq5p74uu34f3\">另請參閱:</p>\n        <ul>\n          <li><a href=\"api/forms/AbstractControl#updateValueAndValidity\"><code>updateValueAndValidity</code></a>\n</li>\n        </ul>\n        </td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>\n        <div class=\"overload-info\">\n  <code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"no-box api-heading\"><a href=\"api/upgrade/static\" class=\"code-anchor\">static</a> <span class=\"member-name\">maxLength</span>(maxLength: number): <a href=\"api/forms/ValidatorFn\" class=\"code-anchor\">ValidatorFn</a></code-example>\n\n  <h6 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"parameters\">引數</h6>\n  <table class=\"is-full-width list-table parameters-table static-method-overload-parameters\">\n  <tbody>\n    <tr class=\"static-method-overload-parameter\">\n      <td class=\"param-name\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"3jftiwvx1g1w9lvblihuzikvy\"><a id=\"\"></a>\n        <code>maxLength</code></td>\n      <td class=\"param-type\"><code>number</code></td>\n      <td class=\"param-description\">\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n  <h6 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"returns\">回傳值</h6>\n  <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"2p9dsof3cr7v7h8jokiggmobu\">如果驗證失敗，則此驗證器函式回傳一個帶有 <code><a href=\"api/forms/MaxLengthValidator\" class=\"code-anchor\">maxlength</a></code> 屬性的對映表（map），否則為 <code>null</code>。</p>\n\n</div>\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td class=\"usage-notes\">\n        <h4 id=\"maxLength-usage-notes\">使用說明<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/forms/Validators#maxLength-usage-notes\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h4>\n        <h5 id=\"validate-that-the-field-has-maximum-of-5-characters\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"53zg50pwr6aczxaw24jbqka7s\">驗證欄位最多有5個字元<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/forms/Validators#validate-that-the-field-has-maximum-of-5-characters\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h5>\n<code-example language=\"typescript\">\nconst control = new <a href=\"api/forms/FormControl\" class=\"code-anchor\">FormControl</a>('Angular', Validators.maxLength(5));\n\nconsole.log(control.errors); // {<a href=\"api/forms/MaxLengthValidator\" class=\"code-anchor\">maxlength</a>: {requiredLength: 5, actualLength: 7}}\n</code-example>\n<code-example language=\"html\">\n&lt;input <a href=\"api/forms/MaxLengthValidator\" class=\"code-anchor\">maxlength</a>=\"5\"&gt;\n</code-example>\n\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n  <a id=\"pattern\"></a>\n<table class=\"is-full-width method-table static-method\">\n  <thead><tr><th>\n    <div class=\"with-github-links\">\n      <h3 id=\"pattern\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"76vga69cfvaddf8rxjmz443xg\">pattern()<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/forms/Validators#pattern\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h3>\n      <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/17.3.0-next.1/packages/forms/src/validators.ts#L342-L394\" aria-label=\"檢視原始碼\" title=\"檢視原始碼\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n    </div>\n  </th></tr></thead>\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <td class=\"short-description\">\n        <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"8l4r4wlapgduw2oulfidonlmn\">此驗證器要求控制元件的值對應某個正則表示式。當使用 HTML5 的 <code><a href=\"api/forms/PatternValidator\" class=\"code-anchor\">pattern</a></code> 屬性時，它也會生效。</p>\n\n        <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"ajvz2kusfoda7eq5p74uu34f3\">另請參閱:</p>\n        <ul>\n          <li><a href=\"api/forms/AbstractControl#updateValueAndValidity\"><code>updateValueAndValidity</code></a>\n</li>\n        </ul>\n        </td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>\n        <div class=\"overload-info\">\n  <code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"no-box api-heading\"><a href=\"api/upgrade/static\" class=\"code-anchor\">static</a> <span class=\"member-name\"><a href=\"api/forms/PatternValidator\" class=\"code-anchor\">pattern</a></span>(<a href=\"api/forms/PatternValidator\" class=\"code-anchor\">pattern</a>: string | RegExp): <a href=\"api/forms/ValidatorFn\" class=\"code-anchor\">ValidatorFn</a></code-example>\n\n  <h6 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"parameters\">引數</h6>\n  <table class=\"is-full-width list-table parameters-table static-method-overload-parameters\">\n  <tbody>\n    <tr class=\"static-method-overload-parameter\">\n      <td class=\"param-name\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"be7rp6vfrk6txo4pp1j7wdbcl\"><a id=\"\"></a>\n        <code><a href=\"api/forms/PatternValidator\" class=\"code-anchor\">pattern</a></code></td>\n      <td class=\"param-type\"><code>string | RegExp</code></td>\n      <td class=\"param-description\">\n        <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"87i9xu6358ayyelmtsn0uo73k\">用於測試值的正則表示式或字串。如果傳遞了字串，會在它前面追加 <code>^</code> 字元，並在後面追加 <code>$</code>\n字元（如果尚不存在），然後使用所得的正則表示式測試這些值。</p>\n\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n  <h6 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"returns\">回傳值</h6>\n  <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"7fh261s7rjagbtevblm301tci\">如果驗證失敗，則此驗證器函式回傳一個帶有 <code><a href=\"api/forms/PatternValidator\" class=\"code-anchor\">pattern</a></code> 屬性的對映表（map），否則為 <code>null</code>。</p>\n\n</div>\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td class=\"usage-notes\">\n        <h4 id=\"pattern-usage-notes\">使用說明<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/forms/Validators#pattern-usage-notes\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h4>\n        <h5 id=\"validate-that-the-field-only-contains-letters-or-spaces\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"b5z2gwe2mcxxg7l2psqhxcg3m\">驗證該欄位只包含字母或空格<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/forms/Validators#validate-that-the-field-only-contains-letters-or-spaces\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h5>\n<code-example language=\"typescript\">\nconst control = new <a href=\"api/forms/FormControl\" class=\"code-anchor\">FormControl</a>('1', Validators.pattern('[a-zA-Z ]*'));\n\nconsole.log(control.errors); // {<a href=\"api/forms/PatternValidator\" class=\"code-anchor\">pattern</a>: {requiredPattern: '^[a-zA-Z ]*$', actualValue: '1'}}\n</code-example>\n<code-example language=\"html\">\n&lt;input <a href=\"api/forms/PatternValidator\" class=\"code-anchor\">pattern</a>=\"[a-zA-Z ]*\"&gt;\n</code-example>\n<h5 id=\"pattern-matching-with-the-global-or-sticky-flag\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"bwvb0ux3cgy1g7xdxwerfez3c\">帶有全域或粘性（sticky）標誌的對應模式<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/forms/Validators#pattern-matching-with-the-global-or-sticky-flag\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h5>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"58psvr7h3dydv1xfnhhywamso\">當要連續執行驗證時，使用傳遞給 <code>Validators.pattern</code> 的 <code>g</code> 或 <code>y</code> 標誌建立的 <code>RegExp</code>\n物件可以在同一輸入上產生不同的結果。這是由於在 <a href=\"https://tc39.es/ecma262/#sec-regexpbuiltinexec\">ECMA-262\n中</a>為 <code>RegExp.prototype.test</code>\n定義的行為（<code>RegExp</code> 保留了最後一個對應項的索引）。由於這種現象，建議你使用\n<code>Validators.pattern</code> 時<strong>不要</strong>傳入啟用了全域或粘性標誌的 <code>RegExp</code>。</p>\n<code-example language=\"typescript\">\n// Not recommended (since the `g` flag is used)\nconst controlOne = new <a href=\"api/forms/FormControl\" class=\"code-anchor\">FormControl</a>('1', Validators.pattern(/foo/g));\n\n// Good\nconst controlTwo = new <a href=\"api/forms/FormControl\" class=\"code-anchor\">FormControl</a>('1', Validators.pattern(/foo/));\n</code-example>\n\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n  <a id=\"nullValidator\"></a>\n<table class=\"is-full-width method-table static-method\">\n  <thead><tr><th>\n    <div class=\"with-github-links\">\n      <h3 id=\"nullvalidator\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"84lgwgr07twj7w1bfxelqtfkw\">nullValidator()<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/forms/Validators#nullvalidator\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h3>\n      <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/17.3.0-next.1/packages/forms/src/validators.ts#L395-L405\" aria-label=\"檢視原始碼\" title=\"檢視原始碼\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n    </div>\n  </th></tr></thead>\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <td class=\"short-description\">\n        <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"56v20telx86a5ynbcdf1iwvqr\">此驗證器什麼也不做。</p>\n\n        <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"ajvz2kusfoda7eq5p74uu34f3\">另請參閱:</p>\n        <ul>\n          <li><a href=\"api/forms/AbstractControl#updateValueAndValidity\"><code>updateValueAndValidity</code></a>\n</li>\n        </ul>\n        </td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>\n        <div class=\"overload-info\">\n  <code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"no-box api-heading\"><a href=\"api/upgrade/static\" class=\"code-anchor\">static</a> <span class=\"member-name\">nullValidator</span>(control: <a href=\"api/forms/AbstractControl\" class=\"code-anchor\">AbstractControl</a>&lt;any, any&gt;): <a href=\"api/forms/ValidationErrors\" class=\"code-anchor\">ValidationErrors</a> | null</code-example>\n\n  <h6 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"parameters\">引數</h6>\n  <table class=\"is-full-width list-table parameters-table static-method-overload-parameters\">\n  <tbody>\n    <tr class=\"static-method-overload-parameter\">\n      <td class=\"param-name\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"96j43ie9c8s2bdcichcwyw0vj\"><a id=\"\"></a>\n        <code>control</code></td>\n      <td class=\"param-type\"><code><a href=\"api/forms/AbstractControl\" class=\"code-anchor\">AbstractControl</a>&lt;any, any&gt;</code></td>\n      <td class=\"param-description\">\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n  <h6 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"returns\">回傳值</h6>\n  <p><code><a href=\"api/forms/ValidationErrors\" class=\"code-anchor\">ValidationErrors</a> | null</code></p>\n\n</div>\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n  <a id=\"compose\"></a>\n<table class=\"is-full-width method-table static-method\">\n  <thead><tr><th>\n    <div class=\"with-github-links\">\n      <h3 id=\"compose\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"cgwyzat7dcgx63g28gvx77uoe\">compose()<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/forms/Validators#compose\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h3>\n      <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/17.3.0-next.1/packages/forms/src/validators.ts#L420-L422\" aria-label=\"檢視原始碼\" title=\"檢視原始碼\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n    </div>\n  </th></tr></thead>\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <td>\n        <div class=\"overload-info\">\n  <div class=\"short-description\">\n    <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"allph1x2jih6rg5p7pdxr3gs9\">把多個驗證器合併成一個函式，它會回傳指定控制元件的各個錯誤對映表的並集。</p>\n\n  </div>\n  <code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"no-box api-heading\"><a href=\"api/upgrade/static\" class=\"code-anchor\">static</a> <span class=\"member-name\">compose</span>(validators: null): null</code-example>\n\n  <h6 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"parameters\">引數</h6>\n  <table class=\"is-full-width list-table parameters-table static-method-overload-parameters\">\n  <tbody>\n    <tr class=\"static-method-overload-parameter\">\n      <td class=\"param-name\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"adwobxp3mn2ye6e6kp9u6ctdw\"><a id=\"\"></a>\n        <code>validators</code></td>\n      <td class=\"param-type\"><code>null</code></td>\n      <td class=\"param-description\">\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n  <h6 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"returns\">回傳值</h6>\n  <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"a4b6m07zit6afklfkmi6tscmi\">如果驗證失敗，則此驗證器函式回傳各個驗證器所回傳錯誤物件的一個並集，否則為 <code>null</code>。</p>\n\n</div>\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>\n        <div class=\"overload-info\">\n  <code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"no-box api-heading\"><a href=\"api/upgrade/static\" class=\"code-anchor\">static</a> <span class=\"member-name\">compose</span>(validators: <a href=\"api/forms/ValidatorFn\" class=\"code-anchor\">ValidatorFn</a>[]): <a href=\"api/forms/ValidatorFn\" class=\"code-anchor\">ValidatorFn</a> | null</code-example>\n\n  <h6 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"parameters\">引數</h6>\n  <table class=\"is-full-width list-table parameters-table static-method-overload-parameters\">\n  <tbody>\n    <tr class=\"static-method-overload-parameter\">\n      <td class=\"param-name\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"adwobxp3mn2ye6e6kp9u6ctdw\"><a id=\"\"></a>\n        <code>validators</code></td>\n      <td class=\"param-type\"><code><a href=\"api/forms/ValidatorFn\" class=\"code-anchor\">ValidatorFn</a>[]</code></td>\n      <td class=\"param-description\">\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n  <h6 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"returns\">回傳值</h6>\n  <p><code><a href=\"api/forms/ValidatorFn\" class=\"code-anchor\">ValidatorFn</a> | null</code></p>\n\n</div>\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n  <a id=\"composeAsync\"></a>\n<table class=\"is-full-width method-table static-method\">\n  <thead><tr><th>\n    <div class=\"with-github-links\">\n      <h3 id=\"composeasync\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"3h0w6e6l2w378qlipfg0lraeh\">composeAsync()<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/forms/Validators#composeasync\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h3>\n      <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/17.3.0-next.1/packages/forms/src/validators.ts#L423-L437\" aria-label=\"檢視原始碼\" title=\"檢視原始碼\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n    </div>\n  </th></tr></thead>\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <td class=\"short-description\">\n        <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"9g4hn5edb9x7irlxka0iyv7hh\">把多個非同步驗證器合併成一個函式，它會回傳指定控制元件的各個錯誤對映表的並集。</p>\n\n        <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"ajvz2kusfoda7eq5p74uu34f3\">另請參閱:</p>\n        <ul>\n          <li><a href=\"api/forms/AbstractControl#updateValueAndValidity\"><code>updateValueAndValidity</code></a>\n</li>\n        </ul>\n        </td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>\n        <div class=\"overload-info\">\n  <code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"no-box api-heading\"><a href=\"api/upgrade/static\" class=\"code-anchor\">static</a> <span class=\"member-name\">composeAsync</span>(validators: <a href=\"api/forms/AsyncValidatorFn\" class=\"code-anchor\">AsyncValidatorFn</a>[]): <a href=\"api/forms/AsyncValidatorFn\" class=\"code-anchor\">AsyncValidatorFn</a> | null</code-example>\n\n  <h6 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"parameters\">引數</h6>\n  <table class=\"is-full-width list-table parameters-table static-method-overload-parameters\">\n  <tbody>\n    <tr class=\"static-method-overload-parameter\">\n      <td class=\"param-name\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"adwobxp3mn2ye6e6kp9u6ctdw\"><a id=\"\"></a>\n        <code>validators</code></td>\n      <td class=\"param-type\"><code><a href=\"api/forms/AsyncValidatorFn\" class=\"code-anchor\">AsyncValidatorFn</a>[]</code></td>\n      <td class=\"param-description\">\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n  <h6 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"returns\">回傳值</h6>\n  <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"6fq6ihydchssthi9rcvufmp5h\">如果驗證失敗，則此驗證器函式回傳各異步驗證器所回傳錯誤物件的一個並集，否則為 <code>null</code>。</p>\n\n</div>\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/forms\n - api/forms/AbstractControl\n - api/forms/EmailValidator\n - api/forms/FormBuilder\n - api/forms/FormControlDirective\n - api/forms/FormControlName\n - api/forms/FormGroupDirective\n - api/forms/FormGroupName\n - guide/dynamic-form\n - guide/form-validation\n - guide/reactive-forms\n-->\n<!-- link